This subpackage (pycse.sklearn.zenn) is a vendored copy of the ZENN project.

Upstream:  https://github.com/WilliamMoriaty/ZENN
License:   MIT
Authors:   ZENN Contributors

Paper:
  Wang, S.; Shang, S.-L.; Liu, Z.-K.; Hao, W. (2026).
  "ZENN: A thermodynamics-inspired computational framework for
  heterogeneous data-driven modeling."
  Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences 123(1): e2511227122.

